main event: Two Air Force pilots locked on a UFO during an Air Intelligence mission.
interesting points: The pilots observed the UFO performing erratic maneuvers which approximated the performance of modern jet aircraft., The UFO executed a sharp 180-degree turn and maintained a high rate of speed during the encounter., Weather conditions were clear at the time of the sighting., The sighting lasted for approximately 4-5 minutes., Several military and civilian observers verified the pilots' observations.
witness description: Two Air Force pilots and radar observers
